15:01.263 --> 15:14.055
University between these environmentalists 
spurred on by people like Cousteau and private

15:01.263 --> 15:14.055
enterprise, which has not won any records in North 
Carolina, by the way, for preserving the

15:01.263 --> 15:14.055
shoreline? That's a sore point. How do you react to 
that? What's your personal reaction to that? To

15:20.582 --> 15:22.543
these two different opinions? To this sort of 
pressure, this internal pressure, if there is

15:22.624 --> 15:26.147
such, created within your state itself. Well, 
without someone like Cousteau to influence the

15:27.700 --> 15:34.407
man in the street, it would be a losing cause. 
