15:36.329 --> 15:44.437
conveying to the man in the street the real 
problems. They're too concerned about the

15:44.457 --> 15:46.319
details. They're not capable of putting it into 
language that people can understand. And it's

15:49.702 --> 15:55.868
going to be up to somebody like Cousteau and Ralph 
Nader to sufficiently aroused the public to

15:56.270 --> 16:03.920
permit the government to do some of the things that 
the scientific community thinks should be done.

16:06.163 --> 16:07.945
What sort of positive steps should we take?

16:11.029 --> 16:11.450
Well...

