16:56.159 --> 17:24.259
their enforcement Well, if they will do this, it 
may be a new day dawning, because right now there

17:24.948 --> 17:42.773
are flagrant violations of existing county 
ordinances on the use of septic tanks, for

17:24.948 --> 17:42.773
example, the development of trailer parks, and 
how many trailers can be attached to a septic tank.

17:43.494 --> 17:48.621
